+# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
+#  Message overrides (built-in translations)
+# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
+# Override any built-in BungeeCord message (the keys from messages.properties)
+# and render it through the full colour pipeline: MiniMessage (RGB, <gradient>,
+# <#hex>) by default, or legacy '&' / section codes incl. hex. Use {NL} for a
+# new line. Overrides are rendered and cached on startup; run
+# "/xwaterfall messages reload" (or "/xwaterfall reload" for everything) to
+# re-read them.
+#
+# Keep positional placeholders like {0} where the original has them. Because
+# these go through java.text.MessageFormat, a literal single quote must be
+# doubled ('') just like in messages.properties.
+#
+# Common keys: proxy_full, outdated_client {0}, outdated_server {0},
+# name_invalid, already_connected_proxy, lost_connection, server_went_down,
+# kick_message, reject_transfer. Leave the section empty to change nothing.
+# Every built-in key is listed below with its default text so you can edit any
+# of them in place. Delete a line to fall back to the built-in default.
